# Starting Points (Link Garden)

Now that you know how to get around, here are some ideas on where you might start!

## Search Engines

Searching for content about something? Try one of these!
(Unlike Google, these won't understand questions - be sure your search includes the actual words that should be in the found pages (and no other words))

=> gemini://tlgs.one "Totally Legit" Gemini Search (for Geminispace)
=> gopher://gopher.floodgap.com/1/v2/ Floodgap/Veronica 2 (for Gopherspace)

## Cities and Tildespaces

Servers with personal sites for a multitude of different users. Like GeoCities of old!

=> gemini://sdf.org/ The Super Dimension Fortress (SDF) - Gemini
=> cophre://sdf.org/1/ The Super Dimension Fortress (SDF) - Gopher
=> gemini://tilde.team/ Tilde Team - Gemini
=> gopher://tilde.team/1/ Tilde Team - Gopher
=> gemini://tilde.team/~khuxkm/leo/ khuxkm's LEO

## Bulletin Boards (BBS)

Servers where you can post and read content on a variety of topics.

=> gemini://bbs.geminispace.org/ GeminiSpace BBS
=> gemini://station.martinrue.com/ Station

## Games, and Gaming Spaces

=> gemini://astrobotany.mozz.us/ Astrobotany (Care for your digital flowers, and participate in a community)
=> gemini://gemini.thegonz.net/ "Things" at TheGonz.net (scroll to the "Games" section)
=> gopher://mozz.us:7006/1/ Text Adventures at Mozz.us (Gopher)
=> gemini://sggs.thegonz.net/ Simple Gemini Game Server (Shogi, Go, Connect4, ...)

